    else
      right; refine ‚ü®x, ?_, y, ?_, by linarith, 2 * j + 1, by ring‚ü© <;> simp_all [hxI, hyI]
  else if hyz : y ‚ąą S ‚ÜĒ z ‚ąą S then
    if hy : y ‚ąą S then
      left; refine ‚ü®y, hy, z, hyz.mp hy, by linarith, 2 * j + 3, by ring‚ü©
    else
